## Language

One heading per concept. State what the term **is**, not what it does. Pick the single
best word for each concept and list every rejected synonym under `_Avoid_`, so reviewers
and agents converge on one vocabulary instead of drifting across near-synonyms.

### {Term}

A {one-to-two-sentence definition of what the term is}. Note any entity it belongs to or
is distinct from, so the boundary is unambiguous.
_Avoid_: {synonym}, {synonym}

